Title: IMPORTANT FROM SOUTH CAROLINA
Abstract: The United States transport Ericsson, Capt. LOWDER from Tortugas 16th inst., Key West 18th and Port Royal 23d, arrived here yesterday morning. She brings a large mail from all the above places, and has 181 passengers, among whom is Gen. BENHAM and Staff.
